query:
SELECT 
  cmlNumber,
  location,
  component,
  componentType,
  tActual
FROM tmlReadings 
WHERE cmlNumber REGEXP '^[0-9]+$'
ORDER BY CAST(cmlNumber AS UNSIGNED)
LIMIT 15;
